{"id": "figure_009", "modality": "figures", "name": "Mixture-of-Experts Layer", "task": {"description": "Create a single 1920x1080 self-contained HTML file using ONLY inline CSS and inline SVG that reproduces a Mixture-of-Experts (MoE) layer figure. Title 'Mixture-of-Experts Layer (Top-2 Gating)' at top in 32px bold. Bottom: an 'Input Token x' box. The token feeds into a 'Gating Network / Router (softmax)' box that outputs gating weights. Draw a horizontal row of EXACTLY SIX 'Expert' FFN boxes ('Expert 1' .. 'Expert 6') above the router. The router dispatches the token to the TOP-2 selected experts (draw SOLID arrows to exactly two highlighted experts, e.g. Expert 2 and Expert 5, and faded/dashed arrows or no arrows to the unselected four). Each selected expert's output multiplies by its gate weight 'g_i' and the selected outputs feed into a 'Weighted Combine (\u03a3 g_i \u00b7 E_i(x))' box at the top producing the output. Annotate the two gate weights (e.g. g_2 = 0.7, g_5 = 0.3). Six experts, top-2 routing. HARDEN (density + alignment): ALSO include (a) a LEGEND box that maps every distinct block color and every arrow/line style used in the figure, and (b) a small tensor-shape annotation on each major block (e.g. 'BxNxd'). Pack the figure densely with at least 14 labeled elements; every group of sibling blocks must be equal-size and share edges, with uniform gutters, and nothing may overlap or clip.", "requirements": ["All components (Input Token, Router/Gating box, exactly SIX Expert boxes, Weighted Combine box) are visible with no clipping at any edge", "No two boxes overlap each other", "Every box label (Expert 1..6, router, combine) is fully contained inside its box with no overflow", "There are EXACTLY six Expert boxes, drawn in an evenly spaced horizontal row", "The router dispatches to EXACTLY TWO experts via solid (selected) arrows, visually distinct from the unselected experts (dashed/faded/no arrow)", "The two selected experts' outputs both connect into the Weighted Combine box, and unselected experts do not connect to it", "Two gate-weight annotations (e.g. g_2, g_5) appear on the correct selected-expert paths and are legible without colliding", "Router-to-expert arrows do not cross through unrelated Expert boxes", "The Weighted Combine box label shows the gated-sum formula (\u03a3 g_i \u00b7 E_i(x)) fully contained", "No element is within 10px of any viewport edge", "No horizontal or vertical scrollbar appears; all content fits inside 1920x1080", "A legend box maps every block color and arrow/line style used; each major block carries a tensor-shape annotation; sibling blocks are equal-size and edge-aligned with uniform gutters; no element overlaps or is clipped"]}, "runs": [{"run": 1, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5273, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 15482}, {"run": 2, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 4739, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 14222}, {"run": 3, "ss_n_defects": 2, "ss_text_overlap": 0, "ss_clipped": 1, "ss_overflow": 0, "ss_total_tokens": 5518, "rv_n_defects": 0, "rv_text_overlap": 0, "rv_clipped": 0, "rv_overflow": 0, "rv_iterations": 2, "rv_total_tokens": 13373}], "ss_img": "images/figures/figure_009_ss.jpg", "rv_img": "images/figures/figure_009_rv.jpg", "ss_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Mixture-of-Experts Layer</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 20px;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <svg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1080\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Title -->\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"50\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"32\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1a1a1a\">\n                Mixture-of-Experts Layer (Top-2 Gating)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Output Box -->\n            <rect x=\"760\" y=\"120\" width=\"400\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#2e7d32\" stroke=\"#1b5e20\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Output\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"170\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#c8e6c9\">\n                BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                Weighted Combine (\u03a3 g_i \u00b7 E_i(x))\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert Boxes -->\n            <!-- Expert 1 -->\n            <rect x=\"160\" y=\"280\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 1\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#757575\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"260\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (Unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 2 (Selected) -->\n            <rect x=\"400\" y=\"280\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1976d2\" stroke=\"#0d47a1\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Expert 2\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#bbdefb\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                FFN (Selected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 3 -->\n            <rect x=\"640\" y=\"280\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"740\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 3\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"740\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#757575\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"740\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (Unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 4 -->\n            <rect x=\"880\" y=\"280\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"980\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 4\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"980\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#757575\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"980\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (Unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 5 (Selected) -->\n            <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"280\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#1976d2\" stroke=\"#0d47a1\" stroke-width=\"3\"/>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Expert 5\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#bbdefb\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                FFN (Selected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 6 -->\n            <rect x=\"1360\" y=\"280\" width=\"200\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 6\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#757575\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1460\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (Unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Gating Network -->\n            <rect x=\"760\" y=\"480\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#f57c00\" stroke=\"#e65100\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"515\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Gating Network / Router\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"535\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#ffe0b2\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNx6\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                (softmax)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Input Token -->\n            <rect x=\"760\" y=\"680\" width=\"400\" height=\"80\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"#6a1b9a\" stroke=\"#4a148c\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"710\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Input Token x\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"730\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#e1bee7\">\n                BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"745\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                Sequence Position\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Gate Weight Annotations -->\n            <text x=\"500\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1976d2\">\n                g\u2082 = 0.7\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1220\" y=\"250\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1976d2\">\n                g\u2085 = 0.3\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrows from Input to Gating -->\n            <path d=\"M 960 680 L 960 580\" stroke=\"#333\" stroke-width=\"3\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Arrows from Gating to Experts (Solid for selected, dashed for unselected) -->\n            <!-- To Expert 1 (unselected) -->\n            <path d=\"M 800 480 L 260 380\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-gray)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 2 (selected) -->\n            <path d=\"M 860 480 L 500 380\" stroke=\"#1976d2\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 3 (unselected) -->\n            <path d=\"M 920 480 L 740 380\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-gray)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 4 (unselected) -->\n            <path d=\"M 1000 480 L 980 380\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-gray)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 5 (selected) -->\n            <path d=\"M 1060 480 L 1220 380\" stroke=\"#1976d2\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 6 (unselected) -->\n            <path d=\"M 1120 480 L 1460 380\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-gray)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Arrows from Selected Experts to Output -->\n            <path d=\"M 500 280 L 860 200\" stroke=\"#2e7d32\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n            <path d=\"M 1220 280 L 1060 200\" stroke=\"#2e7d32\" stroke-width=\"4\" fill=\"none\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Legend Box -->\n            <rect x=\"50\" y=\"800\" width=\"400\" height=\"220\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#333\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"250\" y=\"830\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">\n                LEGEND\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend Items -->\n            <!-- Selected Expert -->\n            <rect x=\"70\" y=\"850\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#1976d2\" stroke=\"#0d47a1\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"867\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Selected Expert (Top-2)</text>\n            \n            <!-- Unselected Expert -->\n            <rect x=\"70\" y=\"885\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"902\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Unselected Expert</text>\n            \n            <!-- Gating Network -->\n            <rect x=\"70\" y=\"920\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#f57c00\" stroke=\"#e65100\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"937\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Gating Network / Router</text>\n            \n            <!-- Input/Output -->\n            <rect x=\"70\" y=\"955\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#6a1b9a\" stroke=\"#4a148c\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"972\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Input Token</text>\n            \n            <rect x=\"70\" y=\"990\" width=\"60\" height=\"25\" rx=\"4\" fill=\"#2e7d32\" stroke=\"#1b5e20\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"150\" y=\"1007\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Output Combination</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow Legend -->\n            <line x1=\"280\" y1=\"862\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"862\" stroke=\"#1976d2\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-blue)\"/>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"867\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Selected Path (Solid)</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"280\" y1=\"897\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"897\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"5,5\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-gray)\"/>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"902\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Unselected Path (Dashed)</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"280\" y1=\"932\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"932\" stroke=\"#2e7d32\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-green)\"/>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"937\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Output Flow</text>\n            \n            <line x1=\"280\" y1=\"967\" x2=\"320\" y2=\"967\" stroke=\"#333\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"330\" y=\"972\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">Standard Flow</text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow Markers -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#333\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-blue\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#1976d2\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-gray\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#9e9e9e\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-green\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2e7d32\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Routing Information Box -->\n            <rect x=\"1470\" y=\"800\" width=\"400\" height=\"220\" rx=\"8\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#333\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n            <text x=\"1670\" y=\"830\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">\n                ROUTING DETAILS\n            </text>\n            \n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"860\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">Top-2 Gating Strategy:</text>\n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"880\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\u2022 Select 2 highest-scoring experts</text>\n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"900\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\u2022 Route token only to selected experts</text>\n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"920\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\u2022 Combine outputs with gate weights</text>\n            \n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"950\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">Gate Weights (Normalized):</text>\n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"970\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\u2022 Expert 2: g\u2082 = 0.7 (70%)</text>\n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"990\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\u2022 Expert 5: g\u2085 = 0.3 (30%)</text>\n            <text x=\"1490\" y=\"1010\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\u2022 Others: g\u2081,\u2083,\u2084,\u2086 = 0.0 (0%)</text>\n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>", "rv_html": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Mixture-of-Experts Layer</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n            background: #f8f9fa;\n            width: 1920px;\n            height: 1080px;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 100%;\n            height: 100%;\n            position: relative;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <svg width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" viewBox=\"0 0 1920 1080\">\n            <!-- Background -->\n            <rect width=\"1920\" height=\"1080\" fill=\"#f8f9fa\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Title -->\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"50\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"32\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1a1a1a\">\n                Mixture-of-Experts Layer (Top-2 Gating)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Output Block -->\n            <rect x=\"760\" y=\"120\" width=\"400\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#2e7d32\" stroke=\"#1b5e20\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Output\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"170\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">\n                BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"185\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                Weighted Combine (\u03a3 g_i \u00b7 E_i(x))\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert Blocks -->\n            <!-- Expert 1 -->\n            <rect x=\"120\" y=\"280\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 1\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"210\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 2 (Selected) -->\n            <rect x=\"320\" y=\"280\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#1976d2\" stroke=\"#0d47a1\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Expert 2\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"410\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">\n                FFN (selected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 3 -->\n            <rect x=\"520\" y=\"280\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 3\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"610\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 4 -->\n            <rect x=\"720\" y=\"280\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 4\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"810\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 5 (Selected) -->\n            <rect x=\"920\" y=\"280\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#1976d2\" stroke=\"#0d47a1\" stroke-width=\"3\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1010\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Expert 5\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1010\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1010\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">\n                FFN (selected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 6 -->\n            <rect x=\"1120\" y=\"280\" width=\"180\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"315\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                Expert 6\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"335\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1210\" y=\"355\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#424242\">\n                FFN (unselected)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Gating Network / Router -->\n            <rect x=\"760\" y=\"480\" width=\"400\" height=\"100\" fill=\"#ff6f00\" stroke=\"#e65100\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"515\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Gating Network / Router\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"535\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">\n                BxNxd \u2192 BxNx6\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"555\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                (softmax)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Input Token -->\n            <rect x=\"760\" y=\"680\" width=\"400\" height=\"80\" fill=\"#6a1b9a\" stroke=\"#4a148c\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"710\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"white\">\n                Input Token x\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"730\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"white\">\n                BxNxd\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"960\" y=\"745\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"white\">\n                (sequence of tokens)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrows from Input to Router -->\n            <defs>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#333\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-selected\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#1976d2\"/>\n                </marker>\n                <marker id=\"arrowhead-combine\" markerWidth=\"10\" markerHeight=\"7\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"3.5\" orient=\"auto\">\n                    <polygon points=\"0 0, 10 3.5, 0 7\" fill=\"#2e7d32\"/>\n                </marker>\n            </defs>\n            \n            <!-- Input to Router -->\n            <line x1=\"960\" y1=\"680\" x2=\"960\" y2=\"590\" stroke=\"#333\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Router to Experts (solid for selected, dashed for unselected) -->\n            <!-- To Expert 1 (unselected) -->\n            <line x1=\"810\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"250\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 2 (selected) -->\n            <line x1=\"860\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"410\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#1976d2\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-selected)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 3 (unselected) -->\n            <line x1=\"910\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"610\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 4 (unselected) -->\n            <line x1=\"960\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"810\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 5 (selected) -->\n            <line x1=\"1010\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"1010\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#1976d2\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-selected)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- To Expert 6 (unselected) -->\n            <line x1=\"1110\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"1170\" y2=\"390\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"8,4\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Selected Experts to Combine -->\n            <!-- Expert 2 to Combine -->\n            <line x1=\"410\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"860\" y2=\"210\" stroke=\"#2e7d32\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-combine)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Expert 5 to Combine -->\n            <line x1=\"1010\" y1=\"280\" x2=\"1060\" y2=\"210\" stroke=\"#2e7d32\" stroke-width=\"4\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-combine)\"/>\n            \n            <!-- Gate Weight Annotations -->\n            <text x=\"520\" y=\"240\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1976d2\">\n                g\u2082 = 0.7\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1120\" y=\"240\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#1976d2\">\n                g\u2085 = 0.3\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend Box -->\n            <rect x=\"1400\" y=\"120\" width=\"470\" height=\"520\" fill=\"white\" stroke=\"#333\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"8\"/>\n            <text x=\"1635\" y=\"150\" text-anchor=\"middle\" font-size=\"18\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">\n                LEGEND\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Legend Items -->\n            <!-- Selected Expert -->\n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"180\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#1976d2\" stroke=\"#0d47a1\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1500\" y=\"200\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Selected Expert (Top-2)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Unselected Expert -->\n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"220\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#e0e0e0\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1500\" y=\"240\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Unselected Expert\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Router -->\n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"260\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#ff6f00\" stroke=\"#e65100\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1500\" y=\"280\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Gating Network/Router\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Input -->\n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"300\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#6a1b9a\" stroke=\"#4a148c\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1500\" y=\"320\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Input Token\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Output -->\n            <rect x=\"1420\" y=\"340\" width=\"60\" height=\"30\" fill=\"#2e7d32\" stroke=\"#1b5e20\" stroke-width=\"2\" rx=\"4\"/>\n            <text x=\"1500\" y=\"360\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Output (Weighted Sum)\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Arrow Types -->\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"400\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Arrow Types:\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Solid Arrow (Selected) -->\n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"420\" x2=\"1470\" y2=\"420\" stroke=\"#1976d2\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-selected)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1480\" y=\"425\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Selected routing path\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Dashed Arrow (Unselected) -->\n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"450\" x2=\"1470\" y2=\"450\" stroke=\"#9e9e9e\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-dasharray=\"6,3\" opacity=\"0.5\"/>\n            <text x=\"1480\" y=\"455\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Unselected routing path\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Combine Arrow -->\n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"480\" x2=\"1470\" y2=\"480\" stroke=\"#2e7d32\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead-combine)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1480\" y=\"485\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Expert output to combiner\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Regular Arrow -->\n            <line x1=\"1420\" y1=\"510\" x2=\"1470\" y2=\"510\" stroke=\"#333\" stroke-width=\"3\" marker-end=\"url(#arrowhead)\"/>\n            <text x=\"1480\" y=\"515\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Standard data flow\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Tensor Shape Annotations -->\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"560\" font-size=\"14\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Tensor Shapes:\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"580\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                B = Batch size\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"600\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                N = Sequence length\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"1420\" y=\"620\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#333\">\n                d = Hidden dimension\n            </text>\n            \n            <!-- Process Flow Annotation -->\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"850\" font-size=\"16\" font-weight=\"bold\" fill=\"#333\">\n                Process Flow:\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"880\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#333\">\n                1. Input token x passes through gating network\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"905\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#333\">\n                2. Router computes softmax weights for all 6 experts\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"930\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#333\">\n                3. Top-2 experts (Expert 2, Expert 5) are selected based on highest weights\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"955\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#333\">\n                4. Selected experts process the token in parallel\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"980\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#333\">\n                5. Expert outputs are weighted by gate values (g\u2082 = 0.7, g\u2085 = 0.3) and combined\n            </text>\n            <text x=\"120\" y=\"1005\" font-size=\"14\" fill=\"#333\">\n                6. Final output: \u03a3 g\u1d62 \u00b7 E\u1d62(x) = 0.7 \u00b7 E\u2082(x) + 0.3 \u00b7 E\u2085(x)\n            </text>\n            \n        </svg>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}